; NAME: [SSS] Bank
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|SpaceToFace

ADDIU SP SP -40
SW RA 36(SP)
SW S4 32(SP)
SW S2 24(SP)
SW S1 28(SP)


; S1 = Bank address
; S2 = Bank loan amount
; S4 = Current Player's Index

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0 

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 8 ; Frames
JAL RotatePlayerModel
LI A2 SpaceToFace

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 8

LI T0 0x800CD096 ; P1 Overworld Location Address
LBU T1 29(S4) ; Player Index
ADDU S1 T0 T1 ; Current Player Overworld Location Address
LBU T1 0(S1) ; Overworld Location Value
BNEZ T1 bowserbank ; If 1, they're in the ocean - call Bowser Bank
NOP

JAL KoopaBank_Function ; Internal Bank Event
NOP

J exit_main
NOP

bowserbank:
LUI T0 hi(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
LWU T1 0(T0) ; Load spaces remaining into T1

BNE T1 R0 PassingEvent ; If there's no spaces remaining
NOP

JAL LandingBowserBank_Event
NOP
J exit_main
NOP

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 -1 ; Idle animation

LI T1 1

NOP

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6

NOP

NOP

SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
